```plantuml
@startuml victorshinya_serverless-chatbot
actor User
participant "IBM Cloud Functions" as ICF
participant "Watson Assistant" as WA
participant "MongoDB" as DB

User -> ICF: Sends message (HTTP request)
activate ICF

ICF -> WA: Forward message (with session context)
activate WA
WA --> ICF: Return response (text + NLU data)
deactivate WA

opt MongoDB enabled
    ICF -> DB: Store conversation (input, output, context)
    activate DB
    DB --> ICF: Storage confirmation
    deactivate DB
end

ICF --> User: Return chatbot response
deactivate ICF
@enduml
```